&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;This position is located in Japan and requires relocating to Japan.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
