&lt;li&gt;Paid training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holidays and vacation periods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Subsidized, company-provided apartment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Subsidized corporate health insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contract completion bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transportation stipend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
